description:
This is the additional puzzle pack for "Jigsaw Masterpieces". The following 10 puzzle images are included.
-The Pianolesson / Henriëtte Ronner-Knip
-The globetrotters / Henriëtte Ronner-Knip
-Making music / Henriëtte Ronner-Knip
-Young Girl and Cat / Émile Munier
-Playful kittens / Carl Reichert
-Der Malerstreit / Carl Reichert
-Ein gefundenes Spielzeug / Carl Reichert
-"Snowball", "Marco" & "Janey" / Charles Burton Barber
-Noble / Charles Burton Barber
-A Family of Pugs / Charles Burton Barber
name: Masterpieces of World  - Dogs and Cats in the Painting -
